	* mpost.c: Fix a bug which I introduced in MetaPost mode (-M option).
	Note that the definition of x, and y in
	pdf_doc_begin_page (scale, x, y) is the negative of those in
	pdf_doc_begin_grabbing (ident, x, y, ...).

