	* spc_pdfm.c:
	  Test implementation of \special{pdf:literal ...}.

	* spc_misc.c:
	  Ignores \special{pos: ...} too.

	* spec-dpx.tex:
	  Modified to fit the changes introduced in 2005-08-08.

